reviewText: excellent quality shows - easy to follow - relaxing to watch
Love the videos.  Informative.  Can't wait to try out the technique.

Gary and Kathwren Jenkins are a team that puts out consistently superior products. Beautiful art simply taught. Gary is so affable that watching the lessons over and over and (heavy sigh) over again is an easy task. Can't say enough good stuff about their art books and DVD's and can't get enough of them.
